{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"bcf7ac9716","title":"把伟大的毛泽东思想的火炬高高举起","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"d28a99f796","index":0,"year":1966,"month":8,"day":null,"articleId":"bcf7ac9716","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"群众运动重要文献","id":"4bd6d6f93a","type":"文稿大类"},{"name":"破四旧","id":"9ec766296f","type":"主题"},{"name":"文章","id":"c9f57d6426","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"毛泽东","id":"dd2b275f6c","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第一版）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":"","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[{"id":"b6ada40272","name":"北京市第一火炬中学火炬战斗小组"}]},"publication_details":{"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"7e84ad1d16","type":"title","text":"把伟大的毛泽东思想的火炬高高举起","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"bcf7ac9716","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"90e7fbdc16","type":"paragraph","text":"把伟大的毛泽东思想的火炬高高举起","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"bcf7ac9716","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c5f870d4a5","type":"paragraph","text":"北京市第一火炬中学    火炬战斗小组","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"bcf7ac9716","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"633259ad0c","type":"paragraph","text":"1966.08.00","index":3,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"bcf7ac9716","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"8f5c4490c1","type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席说：马克思主义的道理，千条万绪，归根结底，就是一句话：造反有理。","index":4,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"bcf7ac9716","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b1c4fe5237","type":"paragraph","text":"无产阶级文化大革命就是要大造资产阶级的反，大造修正主义的反，我们要高举起毛泽东思想的伟大红旗，让毛泽东思想的伟大火炬照亮全北京、全中国、全世界！","index":5,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"bcf7ac9716","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"de92af267f","type":"paragraph","text":"党中央和毛主席在《中国共产党中央委员会关于无产阶级文化大革命的决定》中指出：\"资产阶级虽然已经被推翻，但是，他们企图用剥削阶级的旧思想、旧文化、旧风俗、旧习惯，来腐蚀群众，征服人心，力求达到他们复辟的目的。无产阶级恰恰相反，必须迎头痛击资产阶级在意识形态领域里的一切挑战，用无产阶级自己的新思想，新文化，新风俗、新习惯，来改变整个社会的精神面貌。\"","index":6,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"bcf7ac9716","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"996177f2c2","type":"paragraph","text":"我们坚决响应党中央的号召，高举毛泽东思想的伟大红旗，大造资产阶级之反，大造修正主义之反，把旧思想、旧文化、旧风俗、旧习惯，打它个翻天覆地，打它个落花流水，把资本主义的乌七八糟的东西，横扫得一干二净，杀它个片甲不留。","index":7,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"bcf7ac9716","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"73b8b1f1fb","type":"paragraph","text":"为此，我们高声倡议：","index":8,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"bcf7ac9716","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"08db0581d7","type":"paragraph","text":"让旧的\"宣武\"区滚蛋！把\"宣武\"区改为\"火炬\"区。","index":9,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"bcf7ac9716","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b7e801e407","type":"paragraph","text":"把\"珠市口到广安门\" 改为\"火炬街\"。","index":10,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"bcf7ac9716","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"0e767f7073","type":"paragraph","text":"把\"宣外大街\"改为\"文革街\"。","index":11,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"bcf7ac9716","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"30615892f1","type":"paragraph","text":"把\"牛街\"改为\"团结街\"。","index":12,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"bcf7ac9716","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f24698d434","type":"paragraph","text":"把\"虎坊路\"改为\"工人路\"。","index":13,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"bcf7ac9716","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"82748a0113","type":"paragraph","text":"把全区的中学改为\"火炬一中，火炬二中，……\"。","index":14,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"bcf7ac9716","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"0ea6264699","type":"paragraph","text":"让毛泽东思想的伟大红旗在我区高高飘扬，让伟大的毛泽东思想的火炬在我区熊熊燃起！","index":15,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"bcf7ac9716","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"2dd5fe27bc","type":"paragraph","text":"革命的造反精神万岁！","index":16,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"bcf7ac9716","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"d7c4976b3c","type":"paragraph","text":"伟大的战无不胜的毛泽东思想万岁！","index":17,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"bcf7ac9716","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"92bfb27fdf","type":"paragraph","text":"我们最最敬爱的领袖毛主席万岁！万万岁！","index":18,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"bcf7ac9716","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c563aa62d3","type":"paragraph","text":"北京市第一火炬中学    火炬战斗小组","index":19,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"bcf7ac9716","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"58e2e53b8f","type":"paragraph","text":"（原北京市菜市口中学）","index":20,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"bcf7ac9716","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"897089b8ee","type":"paragraph","text":"（原件为传单，成文时间不清楚，应在１９６６年８月下旬──编者注）","index":21,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"bcf7ac9716","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}